headline: General Mills Invests $54 Million in Expansion of James Ford Bell Technical Center
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, August 26, 2025--General Mills announces a $54 million investment to expand its James Ford Bell Technical Center, a key hub for the company’s innovation capabilities.

headline: A Local Ice-Cream Chain Shows What American Brands Are Doing Wrong in China
summary: Priced at $4 a cup, less than Häagen-Dazs, Mr. Wild Man’s made-in-the-store gelato has shot ahead of its General Mills-owned rival in the past two years.
